column1: Generated Instruction

ECE 6601 was previously offered in the Fall, Spring, and Summer terms. It was taught in the Fall, Spring, and Summer terms. Here's what you'll learn: This course covers the fundamentals of digital signal processing and its applications in communication and control systems.

The course 'Intro Medical Image Processing (ECE4783, 2013 Spring)', taught by Yi Zhang, has an Effectiveness rating of 4.5, which shows that it was well-taught and beneficial. You can take this course in the Spring term of the next academic year.

The System and Controls track is taught Monday and Wednesday from 14:00 to 15:15 and Wednesday from 17:00 to 18:15
The instructor's office is at Miri 418
